description: The Max Green MG1500VA UPS provides reliable power backup for your devices. With a capacity of 1500VA and 900W, it ensures extended battery runtime of up to 120 minutes. It offers 8 outlets with a combination of battery backup and surge protection. Features include simulated sine wave output, automatic voltage regulation, an LED display, and a USB charging port. This UPS operates at a frequency of 50/60 Hz and uses a sealed lead-acid battery. It operates quietly with a noise level of less than 45 dB. The UPS is sleek and compact, weighing 9.8 kg and measuring 340 x 170 x 160 mm.
